<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَنهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٦٤٦ - أَبُو جَهْضَم.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">عَن:</span> ابْن عَبَّاس ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> توفّي النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَأَنا ابْن عشر سِنِين.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>رَوَاهُ شريك , عَن لَيْث عَنهُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أرَاهُ مُوسَى بن سَالم.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>١٦٤٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو جَهْضَم:</span> الهُجَيْمِي.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
